{
  "texts": [
    "In order to utilize both the local and global information in aerial image classification, a new end-to-end global-local attention network is presented in [33].",
    "The local semantic information and the global information are learned by replacing the fully connected layers for VGGNet by a global and local attention branches.",
    "In [34], the authors overcome the problems associated with CNN and the visual attention strategies such as extracting information from the whole scene and the problem of repeated texture and intro-class diversity, respectively.",
    "A new attention deep feature framework is presented, which generates the attention map with multiplicative fusion as a clear input to drive the network focusing on discriminating regions and enhancing the classification accuracy.Authors in [35] adopt the self-attention with a generative adversarial network in which all features locations are exploited to overcome the problem of extracting local spatial features with a lower-resolution map.",
    "Moreover, they used spectral normalization for the generative adversarial network to enhance the training dynamics."
  ]
}